  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "Now thank we all our God, with heart and hands and voices, Who wondrous things has done, in Whom this world rejoices; Who from our mothers&#39; arms has blessed us on our way With countless gifts of love, and still is ours today.",
    "v2": "O may this bounteous God through all our life be near us, With ever joyful hearts and blessed peace to cheer us; And keep us in His grace, and guide us when perplexed; And free us from all ills, in this world and the next!",
    "v3": "All praise and thanks to God the Father now be given; The Son and Him Who reigns with Them in highest Heaven; The one eternal God, Whom earth and Heav&#39;n adore; For thus it was, is now, and shall be evermore."
  },
